---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service" description="Terms of service for Zelnot technology consulting services.">
  <section class="bg-slate-50 section-padding">
    <div class="container-tight">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none">
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8">Last updated: March 2026</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">Services</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
          Zelnot provides technology consulting services including custom software development, 
          software integration, and DevOps consulting. All engagements are governed by individual 
          agreements outlining scope, deliverables, and terms.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">Client Responsibilities</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
          Clients are responsible for providing timely feedback, access to necessary systems and 
          documentation, and payment according to agreed-upon terms.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
          Unless otherwise specified in an engagement agreement, client deliverables become the 
          property of the client upon full payment. Pre-existing materials and general knowledge 
          retained by the consultant are excluded.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">Confidentiality</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
          I treat all client information with strict confidentiality. Proprietary information, 
          source code, and business data are never disclosed to third parties.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
          My liability is limited to the amount paid for services under the specific engagement 
          in question. I am not liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600">
          Questions about these terms? Contact me at <a href="mailto:zelnot@zelnot.com" class="text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700">zelnot@zelnot.com</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
